{"id":41,"date":"2022-12-19T02:32:45","date_gmt":"2022-12-19T02:32:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gaviaspreview.com\/wp\/gowilds\/?page_id=41"},"modified":"2026-01-23T06:08:50","modified_gmt":"2026-01-23T06:08:50","slug":"founder","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.royalstarexpeditions.com\/founder\/","title":{"rendered":"Founder"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"41\" class=\"elementor elementor-41\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-9531a64 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"9531a64\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-0dcee12\" data-id=\"0dcee12\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-032f9b7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-gva-heading-block\" data-id=\"032f9b7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"gva-heading-block.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gva-element-gva-heading-block gva-element\">   <div class=\"align-left style-1 widget gsc-heading box-align-left auto-responsive\">\r\n      <div class=\"content-inner\">\r\n         \r\n                  \r\n         <div class=\"sub-title\"><span class=\"tagline\">WINFRED MBESA MALONZA<\/span><\/div>  \r\n         \r\n                     <h2 class=\"title\">\r\n               <span>Founder & President, Royal Star Expeditions<\/span>\r\n            <\/h2>\r\n                  \r\n         \r\n         \r\n      <\/div>\r\n   <\/div>\r\n<\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6a7795a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6a7795a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Welcome to Royal Star Expeditions! I\u2019m Winfred Mbesa Malonza ( popularly known as Winnie ), the proud founder and president of this vibrant tour operating company based in the heart of Nairobi, Kenya. My passion for travel and adventure ignited this journey, and it continues to inspire every experience we craft for our travellers.<\/p><p>Growing up surrounded by Kenya\u2019s breathtaking landscapes and diverse cultures, I developed an insatiable love for exploring the world around me. From the verdant hills of the Great Rift Valley to the sandy shores of the Indian Ocean, I\u2019ve traversed numerous landscapes, each adventure deepening my appreciation for the richness of our planet.<\/p><p>At Royal Star Expeditions, my team and I believe that travel is not just about reaching a destination but about creating meaningful connections and unforgettable memories. We curate exceptional experiences that immerse our guests in the beauty and culture of Kenya and beyond. Every expedition is thoughtfully designed to showcase the essence of our stunning locales, whether you\u2019re embarking on a thrilling safari, savouring local cuisine, or engaging with the vibrant traditions of our communities.<\/p><p>I invite you to join us on this incredible journey, where adventure awaits at every turn. Together, let\u2019s explore the wonders of our world and create stories that will last a lifetime.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-34a217d\" data-id=\"34a217d\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7740cb7 gallery-spacing-custom elementor-widget eleme